# Smart Context restore (blue sparkle)

When Smart Context / Purchase Insights / FactBox is **collapsed**, the blue sparkle (`FactBoxPaneAiToggle` / `PurchaseAiInsightsRestoreButton`) restores it.

## Placement (required)

1. **Above all body sections** — after Back, status strip, tabs, and validation; **before** the first `ErpCardSection` / line grid / TOTAL panel.
2. **Right-aligned** in `erp-card-form-page__context-restore` (document forms) or the register insights collapsed band (lists).
3. **Never** absolutely position it over TOTAL, lines, or mid-form cards.
4. Prefer shell wiring (`ErpCardFormPage` / `PurchaseRegisterContextPanel`) — do not sprinkle one-off floating sparkles on individual sections.

```text
Back → Status / Tabs → Validation → [✦ restore] → Form sections…
```
